OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA largely dry and bright
OL,6,Fmorning with some sunny spells but
OL,7,Fcloud increases from the south during
OL,8,Fthe afternoon. Outbreaks of
OL,9,Foccasionally heavy rain spreads
OL,10,Ferratically north through later in the
OL,11,Fafternoon.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FHeavy showers with some
OL,14,Fthunder likely to continue through the
OL,15,Fevening, perhaps the far northwest
OL,16,Fremaining dry, strengthening southerly
OL,17,Fwinds and a warm night.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
