OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FCloudy but mostly dry on
OL,6,FSaturday and a very warm day with
OL,7,Fstrong southerly winds, showery rain
OL,8,Fexpected in the afternoon.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FFeeling
OL,11,Fcooler on Sunday and Monday with fresh
OL,12,For strong winds and a few showers but
OL,13,Fa lot of bright weather too. Lighter
OL,14,Fwinds on Tuesday and mainly dry.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
